Invocation Name: r. b. d. outlet
Developer Terms of Use
des:
RBD Outlet provides rare and limited edition shoes, curating fashionable outfits and accessories. Use this skill to ask for current promotions, shipping policy and return policy. 

Here's how you can open this skill 
"Alexa, open RBD Outlet". 

Once inside the skill you can ask 
-What are the current promotions 
-What's your return policy 
-What's your shipping policy.
